DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       Amazon  EC2  Auto Scaling is designed to automatically launch or termi-
       nate EC2 instances based on user-defined  scaling  policies,  scheduled
       actions,  and  health  checks.  Use this service with AWS Auto Scaling,
       Amazon CloudWatch, and Elastic Load Balancing.

       For more information, including information about  granting  IAM  users
       required  permissions  for  Amazon  EC2  Auto  Scaling actions, see the
